<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>
  <body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-details" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <tal:branch-link define="branch context">
    <metal:branch-link use-macro="context/@@+macros/branch-heading-link"/>
  </tal:branch-link>
  <h1>Link to a blueprint</h1>

  <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form">
  </div>

</div><tal:comment condition="nothing"><!-- end main slot --></tal:comment>

<metal:block fill-slot="help">

  <p>Linking a blueprint to a branch is used to indicate that
  the branch is being used to implement the blueprint.</p>

</metal:block><tal:comment condition="nothing"><!-- end help slot --></tal:comment>

</body>
</html>
